description: END. teams up with Reebok for a special two-piece collection inspired by cryptozoology and generational folk tales. The 'Reported Sightings' pack includes the Reebok Beatnik Sandal 'Abominable Snowman,' a unique design that nods to the mythical Yeti. The sandal features a hairy suede upper in an off-white finish, with a fluffy faux fur lining and grey webbing straps at the midfoot and heel. The heel strap features a stitched woven label with dual END. and Reebok branding, while a toothy rubber outsole delivers grippy traction.

description: Introducing the Ghostbusters x Reebok Ecto Boots ‘Ectomobile’! This stylish and functional boot is inspired by the supernatural comedy franchise and is perfect for those who love a good utility boot. The boot features a grey textile upper with tonal nubuck paneling and an abrasion-resistant overlay atop the medial toe. A wraparound translucent TPU heel clip delivers rearfoot stability, while contrasting yellow accents on the toggle laces and mesh tongue add a pop of color. The boot is finished off with a DMX foam midsole for lightweight cushioning.

description: Get your hands on the MISBHV x Reebok Daytona DMX "Cool Shadow"! This sleek and stylish sneaker is a must-have for any fashion-savvy individual. A collaboration between Natalia Maczek"s streetwear brand MISBHV and Reebok, this shoe is sure to turn heads. The semi-translucent zip-up sheath adds a unique and trendy touch, while the 3M reflective paneling and TPU branding make this sneaker pop. The redesigned lacing system provides support and the DMX moving air technology offers cushioned comfort. The icy blue translucent outsole completes the look of this must-have shoe.

description: The Keith Haring x Reebok GL 6000 'Dog and Human Heel Print' is a sneaker that celebrates the iconic street artist and his art. The sneaker features a bright green nylon upper with white side stripes, tonal overlays in leather and suede, and embroidered heel detailing. The signature of the artist is scrawled on the tongue tag and sockliner, while the EVA midsole is color-popped in yellow and orange. The outsole is solid black rubber.

description: The Reebok Club C 85 is a classic sneaker with a modern twist. Its sleek design and comfortable fit make it perfect for everyday wear, while its clean lines and minimalistic details give it a contemporary feel. The upper is made from premium leather, with a die-cut EVA midsole for added support and durability. The rubber outsole is designed for traction and stability, making the Club C 85 ideal for any activity. Whether you're hitting the gym or hitting the town, this sneaker is sure to step up your style game.

The result is a fresh take on the classic Club C model. The shoe is constructed of a smooth leather upper with stitched paneling, and it features a rubber outsole for traction. It was released in May 2019, and it's already becoming a popular choice among sneakerheads. If you're looking for a sneaker that combines the best of both worlds, then this is the one for you.
